release_note: I have made improvements to reduce data usage.
We have fixed the issue where messages pinned with a pin were not displaying.
This update primarily includes internal improvements.
Minor bug fixes and optimizations have been made.
We have fixed a bug that caused the app to crash when attempting to make voice posts.
Fixed an issue where the message list was difficult to update.
We ve fixed a bug where the app was crashing frequently.
Fixed an issue where sending images in DMs would fail and an issue where the number of DM notifications was incorrect.
We have fixed the issue where you couldn t send PNG images via direct messages.
You can now include up to 4 photos in your post only compatible with iOS14 .
A questionnaire function has been added.
You can now operate the app during a call.
Added the ability to favorite users. Also the operation speed has been improved.
Implemented a notification screen for likes and replies. Various other improvements have been made.
You can now see past posts.
Added categories to the bulletin board.
Fixed a bug related to displaying the number of unread items.
The number of unread messages is now displayed in the message list.
A search screen has been implemented.
